modules.description: Extracts BibTeX entries from DBLP by querying author publications, venues, and individual works using a structured API. Operates on data types such as author identifiers, publication titles, and venue names to retrieve and format bibliographic data. Enables direct command-line access to fetch and export references for academic research and citation management.

Provides functions to search for authors, publications, and venues using the DBLP API, returning structured data based on query strings. Operates on typed records representing authors, publications, and venues with fields like names, titles, and identifiers. Enables direct lookup of specific academic entities by name, supporting tasks like citation tracking or bibliography management.
